          "process_md": "> **How to get register**\n\n\n1. Applicant must visit the [official web portal.](https://www.uplmis.in/Guest/frm_createlogin_forlabs.aspx)1. Provide the required details\n\n  - Enter Aadhaar Number.\n  - Choose Circle.\n  - Choose District.\n  - Mobile Number.\n\n1. Submit the registration request.\n\n<br>\n\n> **How to submit the application**\n\n\n1. Applicant must visit the official [web portal](https://www.uplmis.in/Guest/frm_CreateLogin.aspx?type=2).1. Provide the required details\n\n  - Choose Circle.\n  - Choose Scheme name.\n  - Enter Registered Aadhaar Number.\n  - Enter Registered Mobile Number.\n\n1. Click on &quot;Open Application form&quot;.\n1. Provide the required details in application form.\n\n  - Applicant/Worker details\n  - Child details\n  - Bank Account Details\n  - Submit the required documents\n\n1. Submit the application request. \n\n"
        }
